text: Inverness East, Nairn and Lochaber, may refer to: * Inverness East, Nairn and Lochaber (UK Parliament constituency), constituency of the House of Commons of the Parliament of the United Kingdom, at Westminster * Inverness East, Nairn and Lochaber (Scottish Parliament constituency) constituency of the Scottish Parliament, at Holyrood
